## Email Processing Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as iOS App
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Gmail as Gmail API
    participant Queue as Redis Queue
    participant n8n as n8n Workflow
    participant Claude as Claude AI
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    User->>App: Open App
    App->>App: Check Local Cache
    App->>API: Request Sync
    API->>API: Validate JWT
    
    API->>Gmail: Fetch New Emails
    Gmail-->>API: Email Data
    
    API->>DB: Store Email Metadata
    API->>Queue: Queue for AI Processing
    API-->>App: Return New Emails
    
    App->>App: Update Local Cache
    App->>User: Display Emails
    
    Note over Queue,Claude: Async Processing
    
    n8n->>Queue: Poll for Jobs
    Queue-->>n8n: Email to Process
    n8n->>Claude: Categorize Email
    Claude-->>n8n: Category + Confidence
    n8n->>DB: Update Category
    n8n->>API: Notify Completion
    
    API-->>App: Push Update (WebSocket)
    App->>User: Show Category
```

## Authentication Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as iOS App
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Google as Google OAuth
    participant DB as Database
    
    User->>App: Tap "Sign in with Gmail"
    App->>API: Request Auth URL
    API->>API: Generate State Token
    API-->>App: OAuth URL + State
    
    App->>Google: Open OAuth Flow
    User->>Google: Authorize Access
    Google-->>App: Auth Code + State
    
    App->>API: Exchange Code
    API->>API: Verify State
    API->>Google: Exchange for Tokens
    Google-->>API: Access + Refresh Tokens
    
    API->>DB: Store Encrypted Refresh Token
    API->>API: Generate JWT
    API-->>App: JWT + Refresh Token
    
    App->>App: Store in Keychain
    App->>User: Show Inbox
```

